<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Para Xiomara</title>
  <style>
    body {
      background: linear-gradient(to top right, #ffdde1, #ee9ca7);
      font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
      color: #4B2E2E;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      height: 100vh;
      overflow: hidden;
      cursor: url('https://cur.cursors-4u.net/others/oth-2/oth172.cur'), auto;
    }.poema {
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
  padding: 40px;
  border-radius: 30px;
  box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  text-align: center;
  max-width: 700px;
  font-size: 24px;
  line-height: 2;
  letter-spacing: 1.5px;
  animation: fadeIn 2s ease;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}

@keyframes fadeIn {
  0% {opacity: 0; transform: translateY(50px);}
  100% {opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0);}
}

.poema p {
  opacity: 0;
  animation: reveal 1s forwards;
  animation-delay: var(--delay);
}

@keyframes reveal {
  to {
    opacity: 1;
  }
}

.firma {
  margin-top: 40px;
  font-size: 20px;
  color: #7B3F00;
  font-style: italic;
  opacity: 0;
  animation: reveal 1s forwards;
  animation-delay: 5s;
}

.boton-abrazo {
  margin-top: 30px;
  padding: 12px 24px;
  background: #ff69b4;
  color: white;
  border: none;
  border-radius: 30px;
  font-size: 20px;
  cursor: pointer;
  box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255, 105, 180, 0.8);
  transition: background 0.3s, transform 0.3s;
}

.boton-abrazo:hover {
  background: #ff1493;
  transform: scale(1.1);
}

.corazon {
  position: absolute;
  width: 20px;
  height: 20px;
  background: red;
  transform: rotate(45deg);
  animation: flotar 2s ease forwards;
  opacity: 0;
}

.corazon::before, .corazon::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  width: 20px;
  height: 20px;
  background: red;
  border-radius: 50%;
}

.corazon::before {
  top: -10px;
  left: 0;
}

.corazon::after {
  left: -10px;
  top: 0;
}

@keyframes flotar {
  0% {transform: rotate(45deg) translateY(0); opacity: 1;}
  100% {transform: rotate(45deg) translateY(-200px); opacity: 0;}
}

audio {
  position: fixed;
  bottom: 20px;
  left: 20px;
}

.sparkle {
  position: absolute;
  width: 10px;
  height: 10px;
  background: gold;
  border-radius: 50%;
  pointer-events: none;
  animation: sparkle 0.8s linear;
}

@keyframes sparkle {
  from {transform: scale(1); opacity: 1;}
  to {transform: scale(3); opacity: 0;}
}

.aura {
  position: absolute;
  top: 50%;
  left: 50%;
  width: 100vw;
  height: 100vh;
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  border-radius: 50%;
  animation: auraAnimation 5s ease-in-out infinite;
}

@keyframes auraAnimation {
  0% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 0.1; }
  50% { transform: scale(1.1); opacity: 0.3; }
  100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 0.1; }
}

  </style>
</head>
<body><div class="aura"></div>
<div class="poema">
  <p style="--delay: 0s">En el jardín de tus ojos brillantes,<br>
donde florecen mis sueños constantes,<br>
tu risa es la melodía del viento,<br>
y en tu abrazo encuentro el tiempo.</p>  <p style="--delay: 2s">Eres estrella que ilumina mis noches,<br>
cada latido en tus labios se broche,<br>
mi amor, en tus brazos el mundo es perfecto,<br>
contigo a mi lado, todo es un sueño eterno.</p>  <p style="--delay: 4s">Tu esencia es un verso que nunca se apaga,<br>
en cada palabra, el alma se embriaga,<br>
siempre a tu lado, en este viaje sin fin,<br>
mi amor por ti, un hermoso poema sin fin.</p>  <div class="firma">
    Siempre tuyo,<br> Erick
  </div>
  <button class="boton-abrazo" onclick="crearCorazones()">Haz clic para un abrazo virtual</button>
</div><audio autoplay loop controls>
  <source src="https://www.bensound.com/bensound-music/bensound-tomorrow.mp3" type="audio/mp3">
  Tu navegador no soporta audio HTML5.
</audio><script>
  function crearCorazones() {
    for (let i = 0; i < 30; i++) {
      const corazon = document.createElement('div');
      corazon.className = 'corazon';
      corazon.style.left = Math.random() * window.innerWidth + 'px';
      corazon.style.top = Math.random() * window.innerHeight + 'px';
      document.body.appendChild(corazon);
      setTimeout(() => corazon.remove(), 2000);
    }
  }

  document.addEventListener('mousemove', function(e) {
    const sparkle = document.createElement('div');
    sparkle.className = 'sparkle';
    sparkle.style.top = (e.clientY - 5) + 'px';
    sparkle.style.left = (e.clientX - 5) + 'px';
    document.body.appendChild(sparkle);
    setTimeout(() => sparkle.remove(), 800);
  });
</script></body>
